      { en: 'My beauty is so fantastic that no one can think of you at sunrise or sunset." Red shouted out, "I\'m the ruler of you. I\'m the color of life and live. So nobody can take my place." Purple stood up, "I\'m the color of power. People never question me! They just listen and follow." Finally, indigo spoke slowly. "I stand for thought and reflection. Yet all of you just need them." Suddenly, the sky became dark and rain started to pour down. The colors all gathered in fear.', zh: '我的美如此奇妙，在日出和日落时没有人会想起你们。" 红色大声喊道："我是你们的主宰。我是生命和活力的颜色。所以没有人能取代我的位置。" 紫色站起来说："我是权力的颜色。人们从不质疑我！他们只是听从和跟随。" 最后，靛蓝色缓缓开口："我代表思考和反思。而你们所有人都需要它们。" 突然，天空变暗，大雨倾盆而下。所有颜色都惊恐地聚集在一起。' },
      { en: 'Rain began to speak, "Join hands and come to me." The colors did as they were told. Rain added, "Don\'t you know you each are made for a certain purpose? When it rains, appear together to show that you can all live in peace. The rainbow shows the importance of working together."', zh: '大雨开始说话了："拉起手，来到我身边。" 颜色们照做了。大雨补充道："难道你们不知道你们各自都有特定的用途吗？下雨时，你们一起出现，向世人展示你们可以和平共处。彩虹展示了团结协作的重要性。"' }
